<br>
Don't consider the high-end game to be 1/60 of the game for druids who reach it.  Truth is that it likely is more than 50%, and that percentage grows every day. <br>
<br>
For those of us who have played only our druids to 60, and reached 60 long ago, it is fair to say that the high-end raid game has been a substantial percentage of our total game-playing time to date (I've been at the highest level possible for over half of my total game-playing time, for example).  And I believe that most of us expect it to occupy nearly ALL of our playing time in the future....if we continue playing a level 60 druid.<br>
